                    },
                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-24216",
                            "title": "Navigation menu updates",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-24216\" target=\"_blank\">XT-24216</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>The main <b>Finance</b> menu includes functions to view journal entries:</p><ul><li>Accounts payable invoice</li><li>Accounts receivable invoice</li><li>Generate Journal Entries</li><li>Journal entry</li><li>Unbilled accounts payable</li></ul><p>Under the <b>Administration &gt; Feature settings</b> menu, the <b>Finance</b> menu includes functions to manage the follow data:</p><ul><li>Account</li><li>Journal</li><li>Posting class definition</li><li>Posting class</li><li>Journal entry type</li><li>Attribute type</li><li>Attribute</li><li>Dimension type</li><li>Dimension</li></ul>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "type": "group",
                    "title": "Improvements",
                    "taxonomies": {
                        "_type": [
                            "changes"
                        ]
                    },
                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-16829",
                            "title": "Sequence number assignment",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-16829\" target=\"_blank\">XT-16829</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>Under <b>Company data</b>, you can use the <b>Sequence number assignment</b> function for sales invoice documents. You can assign numbers to specific documents for a given legislation, company, and/or site. You can also search for sequence numbers that match this criteria.</p><p>Default sequence numbers are applied if you do not assign specific numbers.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
        },
        {
