                    "content_parts": [
                        {
                            "key": "XT-22621",
                            "title": "Integrate AP/AR invoices with Sage Intacct for UK legislation",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-22621\" target=\"_blank\">XT-22621</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>You can post AP/AR invoices and credit memos for sales and purchasing to Sage Intacct.</p><p>From the <b>Finance</b> menu, you access the related functions to view details and track the status. After an invoice is posted, you can select the <b>Accounting integration reference</b> number to go directly to that invoice in Sage Intacct.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-22619",
                            "title": "UK tax management setup ",
                            "highlight": false,
                            "content_parts": [
                                {
                                    "content": "<a href=\"https://jira.sage.com/browse/XT-22619\" target=\"_blank\">XT-22619</a>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                },
                                {
                                    "content": "<p>For UK legislation, you can set up tax management including tax determination rules, tax calculation, and so on.</p>",
                                    "taxonomies": "all"
                                }
                            ],
                            "taxonomies": {
                                "software": [
                                    "multi-tenant"
                                ],
                                "version": [
                                    "19.0.0"
                                ]
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "key": "XT-20113",
